PLACEHOLDER — DO NOT USE FOR PRODUCTION BUILDS.

Replace this file with the real Ed25519 public key exported from the offline
signing station (see services/updater/README.md for the openssl commands).

Expected content:

    -----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
    MCowBQYDK2VwAyEA<32 base64 chars of the Ed25519 pubkey>=
    -----END PUBLIC KEY-----

Path at runtime after install:
    %ProgramFiles%\OPSQAI\updater\pubkey.pem

If pubkey.pem is missing when build.ps1 runs, the script generates a DEV-ONLY
throwaway key and warns "Do NOT ship this build." A signed v1.0.0 release
requires the real key to be present here BEFORE running build.ps1.
